name: SK00L is a Daydreamer
description:
Since I was a child, I had a dream to be able to explore outer space.

As I grew up, I realized it was not impossible. Because I can be anything, and be wherever I want as long as I can project it in my head.

I am not an astronaut, nor am I a space expert. But I've explored the furthest places in my mind

- SK00L
